{"tid":2249670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"走入美國大學擺陣挑機 Change My Mind","createTime":"2020-10-19T13:08:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T18:25:14.000Z","uid":270889,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1277179acf221dba990628eceb6024eeaf31ac0f","tid":2249670,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:08:10.000Z","msg":"change my mind 基本上就係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jaMF0e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjaMF0e1.jpg&h=7f609233&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實仲有一系列meme<br />\n<br />\npart 1<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LIuXko6xlCg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLIuXko6xlCg&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZqpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=59422c24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LIuXko6xlCg</a><br />\n<br />\n內容其實就係 <br />\n一個右派人士走入(左派為主嘅?)大學挑機<br />\n話就話挑機 其實係<span class=\"orange\">rational conversation</span><br />\n講野<span class=\"orange\">有晒facts &amp; data去support </span>幾時邊個講過咩都有<br />\n除咗之前個黑人哥仔外 呢種<span class=\"orange\">大家都好應該借鏡吓</span><br />\n<br />\n今次topic係圍繞<span class=\"orange\">任命大法官 &amp; pack the court</span><br />\n第一個blondie好多時都係 I feel like.....I don't like her...it's not right...should wait after election<br />\n不過又講唔出點解 最後都話會返去google吓個new judge 算有達成D共識<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二個男仔反重點去咗疫情下派錢<br />\n第三個就精彩 明反侵 又話讚成pack the court<br />\n到比人問咁侵贏係咪可以派多幾個保守派入去 佢又err err err<br />\n<br />\n仲有part 2 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hOGw8rczdvo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhOGw8rczdvo&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZqpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=0705b35f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hOGw8rczdvo</a><br />\n我未睇晒 不過好似好精彩<br />\n呀Kit叫人respect me as an adult <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反面教材 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1ZVcnYyE3TE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1ZVcnYyE3TE&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZqpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=bb3af11c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1ZVcnYyE3TE</a><br />\n根本就一開波已經係恥笑踩場態度 又點會有common ground"},{"pid":"58276e0f9da10c5ae3a67e3adb17b15a4bd16af2","tid":2249670,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:09:16.000Z","msg":"WATCH: &lsquo;Change My Mind&rsquo;: Crowder Dismantles &lsquo;Court Packing&rsquo; Advocate At TCU<br />\n<a href=\"https://editorial.dailywire.com/news/watch-change-my-mind-crowder-dismantles-court-packing-advocate-at-tcu/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feditorial.dailywire.com%2Fnews%2Fwatch-change-my-mind-crowder-dismantles-court-packing-advocate-at-tcu%2F&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZqpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=e2a7d1b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://editorial.dailywire.com/news/watch-change-my-mind-crowder-dismantles-court-packing-advocate-at-tcu/</a>"},{"pid":"247668d2d8933340f6e4646f8e90d61e726d8cc4","tid":2249670,"uid":270889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:13:50.000Z","msg":"上次講開嘅connect do &amp; don't<br />\n<br />\nTwitter國際線要connect真係唔好太上腦<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aEgdeNU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aEgdeNU</a>"},{"pid":"2bdd52bfa6ccbb2d30e1fd66cb8eac81efb22bcb","tid":2249670,"uid":41562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:22:27.000Z","msg":"識野"},{"pid":"d450583b1f2e3e1a78124476d3765d7ddf4d3874","tid":2249670,"uid":270889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2bdd52bfa6ccbb2d30e1fd66cb8eac81efb22bcb","tid":2249670,"uid":41562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep